PART: Recipes
NAME: Recipes
STATUS: draft

DATA: Recipe Book
MARKER: recipe_book
INTENT: holds all recipes and their details
TAGS: #time
---
The app holds a collection of recipes. Each recipe has a title, ingredients, instructions, cooking time, and a rating.

STRUCTURE: Recipe List Screen
MARKER: recipe_list_screen
INTENT: the main screen showing all recipes
TAGS: #list, #search
---
The screen has a header with the app name, a scrollable list of recipe cards, and a search bar at the top.

WHEN: Search Recipe
MARKER: search_recipe
INTENT: user searches for a recipe by title
TAGS: #list, #search, #user
---
When the user types in the search bar, the list of recipes filters to show only those with titles containing the search term. The user sees a list of matching recipes.

ASSERT: Recipe Rating
MARKER: recipe_rating
INTENT: ensure ratings are valid
---
A recipe's rating must be between 1 and 5 stars.

SURFACE: Recipe Card
MARKER: recipe_card
INTENT: labels and text for recipe cards
TAGS: #card
---
The recipe card displays the recipe title, a star rating, and a "Read More" button.